Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂縛柩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來對付他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請你做我的後援
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…砂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來對付他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請當心點 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的攻擊武器是骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像剛才那樣射出自己的骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者從身體裡抽出骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自由地操縱骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂瀑我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如其名 你能操縱砂子是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強對決 我愛羅對君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱砂子形成無懈可擊的防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不是近戰的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 要接近他很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十指穿彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的動作乾脆利落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是位很強的體術高手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻防一體 砂子攻守兼備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 能控制的砂子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕只有葫蘆裡裝的那些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂瀑我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了砂子 你什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪你會背著這麼重的砂子到處走 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是最好的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂時雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平淡無奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有砂子 我什麼都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從泥土裡製造砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說只是彫蟲小技
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的砂子 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把土裡的岩石和礦物碾成砂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把自己的砂子混進去 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就有新的砂子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂瀑我愛羅 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是名不虛傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂瀑送葬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到那傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會想起那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和那傢伙有著同樣的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想確認自己的生存價值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不討厭黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗是養育我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做錯了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有神的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又把我困在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂 現在要用上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我們輝夜一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現在的我唯一能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強大的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有立刻\N在皮層下用骨頭製造出一層膜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃刻間就會被你壓成粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭 那傢伙還真是個怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是副棘手的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太小看你了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不會再被砂子給困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流砂瀑流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這砂子的規模已經無法讓人逃避或抵禦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個地貌完全改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂瀑大葬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我上次交手時相比更強了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 下一次我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個難纏的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示我還有活下去的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始要向霧隱發動夜襲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事件發生後我們困擾了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今正是我們展示恐怖威力的絕好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些傢伙知道我們輝夜一族的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著想那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把出現在你面前的\N霧隱村的傢伙殺光就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按你的本能去行動就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧隱村的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼 再不斬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間呆站著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著和我相同的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我沒遇到再不斬先生之前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠性急的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是這個村子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標就在旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝夜一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能以戰鬥來維持自己的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會以殺戮為樂 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種單純的東西已經跟不上時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把有組織的集團當作對手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算動手 也只是急著送死的蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著的就剩這些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來被包圍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦比想像中的牢固
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 多殺一個是一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我開心一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要戰鬥 自己又是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一無所知 只是一味地戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要用到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為需要 這就是我行動的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不戰鬥就活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白了這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道一族中只有我倖存了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又變得孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤零零的 一味漫無目地徘徊著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的…花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會開在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開在這裡 不可能被人發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去沒什麼意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去也許就會找到有意思的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你找到了那朵花一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我找到了你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然當時大蛇丸大人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人是為了某種目的才降生於這個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定有著什麼重要的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是守護大蛇丸大人以及他的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回來 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 黑乎乎的 什麼也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神比我更炯炯有神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助現在身處黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧…寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡停止不前的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定追不上佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是停下來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會把佐助給帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂縛柩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個形態…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的好厲害 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這種事都辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個遲鈍的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能再出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大蛇丸洗腦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是洗腦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人最瞭解我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這種人知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.04,0:22:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊 早蕨之舞
